question: Rank departments by punctuality score
sql_query:
SELECT TOP 10 Dname,
       AVG(CASE
             WHEN LateArrival = 0
                  OR LateArrival IS NULL THEN 1
             ELSE 0
           END) AS PunctualityScore,
       RANK() OVER (ORDER BY AVG(CASE
                                     WHEN LateArrival = 0
                                          OR LateArrival IS NULL THEN 1
                                     ELSE 0
                                   END) DESC) AS Rank
FROM dbo.vw_CompleteAttendanceReport
WHERE MONTH(ATDate) = MONTH(GETDATE())
  AND YEAR(ATDate) = YEAR(GETDATE())
GROUP BY Dname
ORDER BY PunctualityScore DESC
answer_preview: No results found for your query.
